Package: FIN451Golem
Title: Commodity Futures Curve Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jacob", "Zarowny", , "jzarowny@ualberta.ca")
Description: This package generates a shiny app that can be used to
    compare the historical performance of Brent Crude (CL) and Natural Gas
    (NG) futures contracts. It also includes US Treasury Yields for
    further analysis.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
